### 🛑 `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# Node modules
/node_modules

# Logs
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# OS-specific
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# IDEs
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp

# Build & temp files
dist/
build/
*.bak
*.tmp

# Optional: API key safety (if separated)
.env